results.description_highlighted: ...In Kay Dee Talks we discuss the current happenings in the Tamil society and discuss it critically to provide an alternative view point delivered in Tamil.
results.description_original: Kay Dee Talks is a Tamil podcast started by two friends under the screen name Mr.K and Mr.D. This is a podcast by common men for common people. In Kay Dee Talks we discuss the current happenings in the Tamil society and discuss it critically to provide an alternative view point delivered in Tamil. The podcast is intended to kindle the thoughts of the audiences through engaging conversations. We would let our listeners explore the unheard information from a known fact. We welcome constructive criticism - please comment on your suggestions and thoughts in the platform you are listening.
